title: Rep. Gottheimer, Stimulus, Vaccine Timeline
itunes:title: Rep. Gottheimer, Stimulus, Vaccine Timeline
description:
Guests: Riley Griffin, Bloomberg Health Reporter, Anna Edgerton, Bloomberg Politics Editor, Bloomberg News macro strategist Cameron Crise, Nadeam Elshami, former Chief of Staff to House Democratic Leader Nancy Pelosi, Boyd Matheson, former Chief of Staff for Senator Mike Lee, and Opinion editor at the Deseret News, and Rep. Josh Gottheimer, a Democrat representing the New Jersey's 5th congressional district.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
